<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<base href="/">
<title>Ipefix Payment Solution</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bootstrap-theme.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/application.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/register.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container main">
        <div class="row header">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="boldi light-blue">Ipefix Payment Solution</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form action="{{ generated_link }}" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.name}}" value="{{csrf.name}}">
                <input type="hidden" name="{{csrf.keys.value}}" value="{{csrf.value}}">
                <div class="col-md-6 border-right">
                    <div class="pull-right content-left">
                        <h2 class="dark-blue boldi">Inscription client</h2>
                        <p>
                            Veuillez copier/coller vos clefs publique et privée ici,
                            vous les trouverez dans votre 
                            <a href="https://dashboard.stripe.com/login" target="_blank">Dashboard-Stripe</a>
                            à la rubrique "Développeurs" -> "Clés API".
                        </p>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default btn-sm btn-block bold">Enregistrer</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 border-left">
                    <div class="pull-left content-right">
                            <div class="form-container">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label class="mid-blue">Votre clefs publique:</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="pkey" placeholder="pk_ ..." required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label class="mid-blue">Votre clefs secrète:</label>
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control" name="skey" placeholder="sk_ ..." required>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                <div class="text-center copyr">&copy; Ipefix 2019</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>